William F. Owens, et al., respondents, v. Thomas T. Buckley, appellant. Decided June 16, 1884. Appeal by defendant from order referring the issues in this action to a referee to hear and determine the same, W. P. Prentice, for appellant; John L. Hill, for respon*535dent.

Before Sedgwick, Ch. J., and Ingraham, J.

Memorandum per Curiam.—Order affirmed, with $10 costs and disbursements.
